OL,3,CDisposable vapes ban comes into force
OL,4,C- here's everything you need to know
OL,6,FA ban on disposable vapes has come
OL,7,Finto force in the UK, making it
OL,8,Fillegal for retailers to sell them
OL,9,Fboth in shops and online.
OL,11,FThe change in law is aimed at reducing
OL,12,Fvaping amongst young people, as well
OL,13,Fas the litter they create.
OL,15,FThe ban on disposable vapes - also
OL,16,Fknown as single-use vapes - applies
OL,17,Facross England, Scotland, Wales and
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland, and includes all
OL,19,Fdisposable vapes, whether or not they
OL,20,Fcontain nicotine.
