OL,3,CDisposable vapes ban comes into force
OL,4,C- here's everything you need to know
OL,6,FRetailers are still allowed to sell
OL,7,Freusable vapes.
OL,9,FThe crackdown follows the soaring use
OL,10,Fof disposable vapes in schools and a
OL,11,Fflood of plastic rubbish from the
OL,12,Fdiscarding of the devices.
OL,14,FWhat vapes are banned?
OL,16,FThe government is banning single-use
OL,17,Fvapes - meaning they either have a
OL,18,Fbattery that cannot be recharged or is
OL,19,Fnot refillable.
