OL,6,FThey are typically thrown away with
OL,7,Fgeneral waste in black bins or
OL,8,Flittered rather than recycled.
OL,10,FEven when they are recycled, they need
OL,11,Fto be taken apart by hand, while their
OL,12,Fbatteries are a fire risk to recycling
OL,13,Ffacilities and can leak harmful
OL,14,Fchemicals into the environment.
OL,16,FA reusable vape has a rechargeable
OL,17,Fbattery and a refillable container
OL,18,Fthat holds the vaping e-liquid.
OL,20,FWhy has the government banned them?
