OL,3,CDisposable vapes ban comes into force
OL,4,C- here's everything you need to know
OL,6,FThe change in law has been brought in
OL,7,Fto prevent the environmental damage
OL,8,Fcaused by vapes, while addressing
OL,9,Fhealth concerns from inhaling nicotine.
OL,11,FIn 2023, up to five million single-use
OL,12,Fvapes were estimated to be either
OL,13,Flittered or thrown away every week in
OL,14,Fthe UK ` almost four times as many as
OL,15,Fthe previous year.
