OL,3,CDisposable vapes ban comes into force
OL,4,C- here's everything you need to know
OL,6,FDepartment for Environment, Food and
OL,7,FRural Affairs (Defra) said England's
OL,8,Fvape usage had grown by more than 400%
OL,9,Fbetween 2012 and 2023, with 9.1% of
OL,10,FBrits now buying and using the
OL,11,Fproducts.
OL,13,FFigures from the charity Action on
OL,14,FSmoking and Health (Ash) suggest the
OL,15,Fnumber of vapers in Great Britain who
OL,16,Fmainly use single-use devices fell
OL,17,Ffrom 30% in 2024 to 24% in 2025, while
OL,18,Fthe use of disposables by 18 to 24-
OL,19,Fyear-old vapers fell from 52% in 2024
OL,20,Fto 40% in 2025.
