OL,3,CDisposable vapes ban comes into force
OL,4,C- here's everything you need to know
OL,6,FDefra said usage among young vapers
OL,7,Fremained too high, and the ban would
OL,8,F"put an end to their alarming rise in
OL,9,Fschool playgrounds and the avalanche
OL,10,Fof rubbish flooding the nation's
OL,11,Fstreets".
OL,13,FCircular economy minister Mary Creagh
OL,14,Fsaid: "For too long, single-use vapes
OL,15,Fhave blighted our streets as litter
OL,16,Fand hooked our children on nicotine.
OL,17,FThat ends today.
OL,19,F"The Government calls time on these
OL,20,Fnasty devices."
