OL,6,FWhat will happen to retailers that
OL,7,Fcontinue to sell them?
OL,9,FRogue traders who continue to sell
OL,10,Fthem risk a fine of #200 in the first
OL,11,Finstance, followed by an unlimited
OL,12,Ffine or jail time for repeat offending.
OL,14,FHow else is the government toughening
OL,15,Fsmoking laws?
OL,17,FThe separate Tobacco and Vapes Bill,
OL,18,Faimed at creating the "first smoke-
OL,19,Ffree generation," is currently working
OL,20,Fits way through Parliament.
